result.name: The Peak Lookout

reviews.text: We were a group of 11 of different nationalities and we booked over the phone we arrived there at sunset, location and view are fascinating fresh air with the clouds close to you , restaurant staff were closing the outdoor area claiming that wind may lead to some issues with the trees which was not clear enough for us. food is of good taste like butter chicken other menu items may be not that good waiters need to speak better English overall experience is nice
Love going there as it is a unique place, lot of history, fantastic view... but terrible service. First served in a table of 10 is already finished when the last guest is finally served.
Food quality are really terrible.... even the dishes with the chef symbol..... don't know how this freaking place survive for many years...
Superb curry served although price is a bit high

Lucky to be able to find a table without booking.
Ordered the chef’s recommended Hanan-chicken rice.  It has garlic in the rice; rather unexpected.  Personally, I don’t like it.

result.adr_address: 香港山頂山頂道121號
result.name: 太平山餐廳

reviews.text: 好吃😋但是份量有點少～
環境是不錯，但服務態度其差無比，對比之下，顯得服務生爛到無法用言語形容，尤其是男性服務生！簡直瞎到爆！自稱自己就是老闆，嗆人：吃不吃隨你，不吃拉倒！有一屁股氣想發火的人，建議可以去這間，保證讓你罵飽罵爽！

有100年以上的餐廳怎麼能不來感受一下
舊時代的痕跡
老闆一定是很有愛
因為服務生還有一位是年紀應該有70歲吧！
身着白色制服黑色西裝褲
搭配著百年餐廳
讓人覺得很有味道

漢堡餐點價格238港幣
雖然不便宜
但是既然都花了時間上來太平山頂
就再放輕鬆欣賞吧！

We were a group of 11 of different nationalities and we booked over the phone we arrived there at sunset, location and view are fascinating fresh air with the clouds close to you , restaurant staff were closing the outdoor area claiming that wind may lead to some issues with the trees which was not clear enough for us. food is of good taste like butter chicken other menu items may be not that good waiters need to speak better English overall experience is nice
環境唔錯，夠哂情調，食物質素又好！🤗
